{"tid":1384262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工不應設下期限","createTime":"2019-07-30T01:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:45:41.000Z","uid":278288,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f039f65ed424b7842a4bc65e1face23ccf0cd922","tid":1384262,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"罷工係我地迫政府跪低嘅籌碼<br />\n相信冇人聽過其他國家罷工係政府寸步不讓，人民先行自動返工<br />\n一日對政府施加壓力有限，等如放多咗日風假或者公假<br />\n希望大家調節心態，8月5政府若然唔回應，應該設下死線升級為無限期罷工，地鐵全線推行不合作運動<br />\n又或者只係維持有限度運作，隔日罷工、逢一三五罷工等等<br />\n<br />\n另外，罷工係極需要人數支持嘅行動，唔係只變成示弱<br />\n希望大家同身邊人做好文宣，唔好以為香港人已經熱情冷卻<br />\n 爭氣呀香港人！！！"},{"pid":"40bd696eea1df536b3213f260096fbd3dc70d1ea","tid":1384262,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:11:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c050650ec9e56d8d4261f8846d36624060a40963","tid":1384262,"uid":278288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"推到全港無限期罷工"},{"pid":"baca44ef2b47bb00958ecf2be6e9734609fb53b8","tid":1384262,"uid":278288,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:12:35.000Z","msg":"當大家宣傳無限期罷工 自然多咗人覺得好應該至少參加一日罷工"},{"pid":"adccc31250019aea40ab2ecc29ed9ef284468cd4","tid":1384262,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:13:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">四天工作制</span>"},{"pid":"f48b215d47f303212a3dad0cc27b5bf1371dca6a","tid":1384262,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:18:18.000Z","msg":"三天工作制"},{"pid":"bd6ebcd39feec0dc52192a149ef24c2b3553180b","tid":1384262,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:18:38.000Z","msg":"兩天工作制"},{"pid":"0ed652dbcfc185d0c160211a06cbdde22b0cd55e","tid":1384262,"uid":278288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:21:02.000Z","msg":"一天工作制"},{"pid":"e495db62aea525f0c05dbb681dc89bebb9c3424f","tid":1384262,"uid":278288,"like":1,"